    {
      "id": "PopularPost198723",
      "post_content": "The real gem here is attaching this to a Zombie with an [Undead Alchemist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Undead Alchemist) on the board.  \nAttack > mill a creature or two and a land > put zombies into play > if the zombie connects, mill some more cards for more zombies. Once you have enough zombies. [Unsummon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Unsummon) the Alchemist.  \n  \n@ Alsebra:   \nNote: the land that gets revealed gets put into the graveyard as well.  \n  \n@ Faralay:  \nThat's his point. Trepanation blade fills your opponents graveyard with useful stuff. ((defending player))",
      "posted_by": "roguepariah",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost198723\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">The real gem here is attaching this to a Zombie with an <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Undead Alchemist\">Undead Alchemist</a> on the board.<br/>Attack &gt; mill a creature or two and a land &gt; put zombies into play &gt; if the zombie connects, mill some more cards for more zombies. Once you have enough zombies. <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Unsummon\">Unsummon</a> the Alchemist.<br/><br/>@ Alsebra:   <br/>Note: the land that gets revealed gets put into the graveyard as well.<br/><br/>@ Faralay:<br/>That's his point. Trepanation blade fills your opponents graveyard with useful stuff. ((defending player))</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy36774\">roguepariah</span>\r\n                                (9/23/2011 10:36:56 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_post